# Whitelist approach: ignore EVERYTHING in this folder by default,
# then explicitly allow only the Vaelo app files. This keeps personal
# files (PDFs, chats, other clients' sheets) and the private sync
# config out of the repo.

/*

# --- allow only these ---
!/.gitignore
!/index.html
!/vaelo-login.html
!/vaelo-content.html
!/vaelo-ops.html
!/vaelo-apps-script.gs
!/VAELO-SYNC-SETUP.md
!/README.md

# vaelo-config.js is intentionally NOT allowed here — it holds the
# private sync URL and must never be committed.
